'''VRChat Home''' is the default Home [[Special:MyLanguage/worlds|world]], created by VRChat. You can access the VRChat Home, by opening your [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu|Quick Menu]] and clicking the '''Go Home''' tile, and choosing '''Default.''' To choose a new Home world, search for a world in the World tab, and choose the '''Make Home''' button. You can go there when you load into VRChat or click the '''Go Home''' button and choose '''Yes'''. You can reset your Home World by searching your Home World in the World tab and choosing the '''Reset Home''' button.